ActPilotage Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Pacific Pilotage Tariff Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE PACIFIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS will adjust its general tariffs of pilotage charges relating to vessels over 226 m in length and the unit calcualtion for these vessels by including an amount based on gross tonnage in the calculation of the tariff.
